      <title>碧桂园债券持有人同意延期兑付人民币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/country-garden-bondholders-approve-delays-on-yuan-bond-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，碧桂园控股有限公司已获得债券持有人的批准，将其九元人民币债券的偿付期限推迟六个月，从而使该开发商有更多时间规划境内债务重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/country-garden-bondholders-approve-delays-on-yuan-bond-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:33:13 GMT</pubDate>
