      <title>中国考虑向顶级银行注资 1420 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/china-weighs-injecting-142-billion-of-capital-into-top-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国正考虑向其最大的国有银行注入高达 1 万亿元人民币（1420 亿美元）的资本，以增强其支持陷入困境的经济的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/china-weighs-injecting-142-billion-of-capital-into-top-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 01:56:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新世界集团因首席执行官郑志刚辞职而暂停交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/new-world-development-halts-trading-amid-ceo-departure-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，新世界发展有限公司首席执行官郑志刚 (Adrian Cheng) 即将辞去该公司首席执行官一职，此后，该公司股票于周四上午在香港暂停交易。这家负债累累的开发商，其首席执行官郑志刚将于周四辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/new-world-development-halts-trading-amid-ceo-departure-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 00:53:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收购公司提高韩国锌业的收购报价，将公司估值提高至 116 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/mbk-raises-korea-zinc-offer-price-to-attract-more-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MBK Partners 将其对韩国锌业公司控制权的主动出价提高了约 14%，推动该股创下历史新高，对这家全球最大锌冶炼厂的估值达到 15.5 万亿韩元（116 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/mbk-raises-korea-zinc-offer-price-to-attract-more-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:59:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>有迹象显示利比亚可能很快恢复生产，油价持续大幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-26</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利比亚各派就欧佩克成员国央行领导权达成“妥协”，为恢复部分原油生产铺平了道路，油价在两周内最大跌幅之后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-26</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:30:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
